document_data.History:
The Thayan shipyards of Alaor were greatly damaged during the [[Salamander War]] in the [[1357 DR|Year of the Prince, 1357 DR]].

However, the [[House of Holy Tides]] survived the great wave and went on to take power on Alaor and turned the main island into a free state for some time. By [[1368 DR]], both islands had been reclaimed by Thay and the [[Red Wizards]].

